text: Nicholas D'Agosto (born April 17, 1980) is an American actor. He is known for being the lead of Final Destination 5. He starred in the Showtime series Masters of Sex and the Fox series Gotham. ==References== Category:1980 births Category:Living people Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:American stage actors Category:American voice actors Category:Actors from Omaha, Nebraska
